    <h2>💎 Why Are So Many Gemstones Found in Poor Countries?</h2>

    <figure>
      <img src="/images/hands-holding-rough-gems.jpg" alt="Hands holding rough gemstones" loading="lazy" />
      <figcaption>Gem buyers often evaluate rough stones in the field before cutting or polishing begins.</figcaption>
